"Latent factor variances and their moderation effects. Estimates are on the "
"log scale internally and back-transformed for display. Significant "
"moderation indicates that the spread of the latent trait changes across the "
"moderator."
msgstr ""

msgid "Factor Means"
msgstr "Medias de Factores"

msgid ""
"Latent factor means and their moderation effects. Significant moderation "
"indicates that the average level of the latent trait differs across the "
"moderator."
msgstr ""

msgid "Factor Covariances"
msgstr "Covarianzas de Factores"

msgid ""
"Latent factor covariances and their moderation effects. Significant "
"moderation indicates that the relationship between latent factors varies "
"across the moderator."
msgstr ""

