"No se pueden calcular los Criterios de Selección de modelos para el grupo "
"%1$s: %2$s"

msgid "At least one result is inadmissible."
msgstr "Al menos un resultado no es admisible."

msgid "Denotes the fit of the model including a saturated structural model."
msgstr "Denota el ajuste del modelo incluyendo un modelo estructural saturado."

msgid ""
"Parameter estimates for the PLS-SEM model, including outer weights, outer "
"loadings, inner model path coefficients, total effects, and residual "
"correlations."
msgstr ""

msgid "Weights"
msgstr "Ponderaciones"

msgid ""
"Outer weights relating observed indicators to their composite constructs. "
"Weights determine how indicators are combined to form construct scores and "
"reflect each indicator's relative contribution."
msgstr ""

msgid "Construct"
msgstr "Constructo"

msgid ""
"Outer loadings (correlations) between indicators and their constructs. "
"Loadings above 0.708 indicate that the construct explains more than 50%% of "
"the indicator's variance."
msgstr ""

msgid "Regression Coefficients"
msgstr "Coeficientes de Regresión"

msgid ""
"Inner model path coefficients between constructs. The f² effect size "
"indicates the substantive impact of removing each predictor: 0.02 (small), "
"0.15 (medium), 0.35 (large)."
msgstr ""

msgid "Outcome"
msgstr "Resultado"

msgid ""
"Total effects combining direct and all indirect paths between constructs."
msgstr ""

msgid "Residual Correlations"
msgstr "Correlaciones de los errores"

msgid ""
"Residual correlations between indicators after accounting for the construct "
"model. These represent correlated measurement errors between indicator pairs."
msgstr ""

msgid "VIF"
msgstr "FIV"

msgid "VIF could not be computed."
msgstr "No se pueden calcular los FIV."

msgid "Endogenous Indicator Prediction"
msgstr "Predicción de Indicadores Endógenos"

msgid ""
"Cross-validated prediction of endogenous indicators using PLSpredict. The "
"prediction metrics assess how well the PLS-SEM model predicts indicator "
"scores out of sample."
msgstr ""

msgid "Prediction Metrics"
msgstr "Métricas de Predicción"

msgid ""
"MAE (mean absolute error), RMSE (root mean squared error), and Q² prediction "
"metrics for endogenous indicators. Q² > 0 indicates that prediction error is "
"less than using the training sample mean. When benchmarks are included, "
"lower MAE/RMSE than the benchmark suggests the PLS-SEM model predicts better."
msgstr ""

msgid "Target MAE"
msgstr "EAM (MAE) objetivo"

msgid "LM MAE"
msgstr "EAM (MAE) de ML"

msgid "GSCA MAE"
msgstr "EAM (MAE) de GSCA"

msgid "PCA MAE"
msgstr "EAM (MAE) de CP (PCA)"

msgid "MAXVAR MAE"
msgstr "EAM (MAE) de MAXVAR"

