msgstr "Mensaje de fallo de la predicción: %1$s"

msgid "Additional Fit Measures"
msgstr "Medidas de Ajuste Adicionales"

msgid ""
"Additional model fit measures for PLS-SEM. Includes CFI, GFI, RMSEA, SRMR "
"for the model-implied indicator correlation matrix, Goodness-of-Fit (GoF) as "
"geometric mean of AVE and R², and bootstrap-based distance measures (dG, dL, "
