msgstr "No se puede calcular la evaluación de modelos para el grupo %1$s: %2$s"

msgid ""
"R² and adjusted R² for each endogenous construct. R² represents the "
"proportion of variance in the construct explained by its predictors in the "
"structural model. Values of 0.75, 0.50, and 0.25 are considered substantial, "
"moderate, and weak."
msgstr ""

