msgstr ""

msgid "Reliability Measures"
msgstr "Medidas de Fiabilidad"

msgid ""
"Construct reliability measures. Cronbach's α assumes equal indicator weights "
"(tau-equivalence). Jöreskog's ρ uses the outer loadings and is the preferred "
"measure for PLS-SEM. Dijkstra-Henseler's ρ_A is a consistent reliability "
"estimate. Values above 0.70 indicate acceptable reliability."
msgstr ""

